column4: Vianocturna85 another thing to keep in mind that just because you can log onto any port at home, many IPs use their own ports. I had that happen with my IP. They never told me that Comcast SMTP port was on port 587.
you can always teach us then :)
like , alls good from your side?
i am in favour of it , but i think it should be left upto the user to decide :)
